" />"},{"pid":"aa7aafb3033c1f1a4219c77bae6ce81690ea9155","tid":752532,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"大眾背後係咩老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96af8099fb71ce6e6c1ff1dd7f162cbbaa5dcfff","tid":752532,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37b8022ed6f8e46e2ca04b1a749bf4572aa8dd75","tid":752532,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"411f13d9b9e96ea65ababe19501c862e509ac082","tid":752532,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"想問問中小學係咪一定要經三聯商務中華買書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果可以係呢到入手<br />\n我覺得會大效果好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"唔係 仲有天利行 大眾 仲有唔小細鋪（老字號）<br />\n不過本身出版商係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"應該都係朗文 現代 果堆？<br />\n<br />\n之前睇過數據，講三中商既盈利中，有3成到係來自教科書<br />\n如果可以係呢到削弱，咁會係一樣好事"}]}